trans-unit.source: Serves as the base class for classes that provides access to session-state values, session-level settings, and lifetime management methods.
The <xref:System.Web.HttpSessionStateBase> class is an abstract class that contains the same members as the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState> class.
trans-unit.target: Die <xref:System.Web.HttpSessionStateBase> Klasse ist eine abstrakte Klasse, die dieselben Member wie enthält die <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState> Klasse.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.HttpSessionStateBase> class enables you to create derived classes that are like the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState> class, but that you can customize and that work outside the ASP.NET pipeline.
trans-unit.target: Die <xref:System.Web.HttpSessionStateBase> -Klasse können Sie abgeleitete Klassen erstellen, die auch die <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState> -Klasse jedoch, die Sie anpassen können und außerhalb der ASP.NET-Pipeline arbeiten.

trans-unit.source: When you perform unit testing, you typically use a derived class to implement members with customized behavior that fulfills the scenario you are testing.
trans-unit.target: Beim Ausführen von Komponententests verwenden Sie in der Regel eine abgeleitete Klasse auf um Member mit angepasstem Verhalten zu implementieren, die das Szenario erfüllt, das Sie testen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.HttpSessionStateWrapper> class derives from the <xref:System.Web.HttpSessionStateBase> class.
trans-unit.target: Die <xref:System.Web.HttpSessionStateWrapper>-Klasse wird aus der <xref:System.Web.HttpSessionStateBase>-Klasse abgeleitet.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.HttpSessionStateWrapper> class serves as a wrapper for the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState> class.
trans-unit.target: Die <xref:System.Web.HttpSessionStateWrapper> Klasse dient als Wrapper für die <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState> Klasse.

trans-unit.source: At run time, you typically use an instance of the <xref:System.Web.HttpSessionStateWrapper> class to call members of the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState> object.
trans-unit.target: Zur Laufzeit verwenden Sie in der Regel eine Instanz von der <xref:System.Web.HttpSessionStateWrapper> zum Aufrufen von Membern der Klasse die <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionState> Objekt.

trans-unit.source: Initializes the class for use by an inherited class instance.
This constructor can only be called by an inherited class.
When overridden in a derived class, cancels the current session.
Always.
The name of the item to add to the session-state collection.
The value of the item to add to the session-state collection.
When overridden in a derived class, adds an item to the session-state collection.
Always.
When overridden in a derived class, removes all keys and values from the session-state collection.
Always.
When overridden in a derived class, gets or sets the character-set identifier for the current session.
The character-set identifier for the current session.
trans-unit.target: Der Zeichensatzbezeichner für die aktuelle Sitzung.

trans-unit.source: Always.
When overridden in a derived class, gets a reference to the current session-state object.
The current session-state object.
trans-unit.target: Das aktuelle Sitzungszustandsobjekt.

trans-unit.source: Always.
When overridden in a derived class, gets a value that indicates whether the application is configured for cookieless sessions.
One of the cookie-mode values that indicate whether the application is configured for cookieless sessions.
trans-unit.target: Einer der Cookiemoduswerte, der angibt, ob die Anwendung für Sitzungen ohne Cookies konfiguriert ist.

trans-unit.source: Always.
The array to copy session values to.
The zero-based index in <c>array</c> at which copying starts.
When overridden in a derived class, copies the collection of session-state values to a one-dimensional array, starting at the specified index in the array.
Always.
When overridden in a derived class, gets the number of items in the session-state collection.
The number of items in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Die Anzahl der Elemente in der Auflistung.

trans-unit.source: Always.
When overridden in a derived class, returns an enumerator that can be used to read all the session-state variable names in the current session.
An enumerator that can iterate through the variable names in the session-state collection.
Always.
When overridden in a derived class, gets a value that indicates whether the session ID is embedded in the URL.
<see langword="true" /> if the session ID is embedded in the URL; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> Wenn die Sitzungs-ID in die URL eingebettet ist andernfalls <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Always.
When overridden in a derived class, gets a value that indicates whether the session was created during the current request.
<see langword="true" /> if the session was created during the current request; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> Wenn die Sitzung während der aktuellen Anforderung erstellt wurde. andernfalls <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Always.
When overridden in a derived class, gets a value that indicates whether the session is read-only.
<see langword="true" /> if the session is read-only; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> Wenn die Sitzung schreibgeschützt ist. andernfalls <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Always.
When overridden in a derived class, gets a value that indicates whether access to the collection of session-state values is synchronized (thread safe).
<see langword="true" /> if access to the collection is synchronized (thread safe); otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> Wenn der Zugriff auf die Auflistung synchronisiert (threadsicher) ist andernfalls <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Always.
When overridden in a derived class, gets or sets individual session values.
The index of the session value.
When overridden in a derived class, gets or sets a session value by using the specified index.
The session-state value that is stored at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: Der am angegebenen Index gespeicherte Sitzungszustandswert.

trans-unit.source: Always.
The key name of the session value.
When overridden in a derived class, gets or sets a session value by using the specified name.
The session-state value that has the specified name, or <see langword="null" /> if the item does not exist.
trans-unit.target: Der sitzungsstatuswert mit dem angegebenen Namen ab oder <see langword="null" /> , wenn das Element nicht vorhanden ist.

trans-unit.source: Always.
When overridden in a derived class, gets a collection of the keys for all values that are stored in the session-state collection.
The session keys.
trans-unit.target: Die Sitzungsschlüssel.

trans-unit.source: Always.
When overridden in a derived class, gets or sets the locale identifier (LCID) of the current session.
The LCID (culture) of the current session.
trans-unit.target: Die LCID (Kultur) der aktuellen Sitzung.

trans-unit.source: Always.
When overridden in a derived class, gets the current session-state mode.
The session-state mode.
trans-unit.target: Der Sitzungszustandsmodus.

trans-unit.source: Always.
The name of the item to delete from the session-state collection.
When overridden in a derived class, deletes an item from the session-state collection.
Always.
When overridden in a derived class, removes all keys and values from the session-state collection.
This method performs the same function as the <xref:System.Web.HttpSessionStateBase.Clear%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Diese Methode führt die gleiche Funktion wie die <xref:System.Web.HttpSessionStateBase.Clear%2A> Methode.

trans-unit.source: Always.
The index of the item to remove from the session-state collection.
When overridden in a derived class, deletes the item at the specified index from the session-state collection.
Always.
When overridden in a derived class, gets the unique identifier for the session.
The unique session identifier.
trans-unit.target: Der eindeutige Sitzungsbezeichner.

trans-unit.source: Always.

When overridden in a derived class, gets a collection of objects that are declared by <see langword="object" /> elements that are marked as server controls and scoped to the current session in the application's Global.asax file.
The objects that are declared in the Global.asax file.
trans-unit.target: Die in der Global.asax-Datei deklarierten Objekte.

trans-unit.source: Always.
When overridden in a derived class, gets an object that can be used to synchronize access to the collection of session-state values.
An object that can be used to synchronize access to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Ein Objekt, mit dem der Zugriff auf die Auflistung synchronisiert werden kann.

trans-unit.source: Always.
When overridden in a derived class, gets or sets the time, in minutes, that can elapse between requests before the session-state provider ends the session.
The time-out period, in minutes.
trans-unit.target: Der Timeoutzeitraum, in Minuten.

trans-unit.source: Always.
